sentences: Christopher Reginald Travis (born December 2, 1993) is an American rapper and record producer from Orange Mound, Memphis, Tennessee.
He began his career in 2012 as a solo artist on YouTube and later on became a member of SpaceGhostPurrp's Raider Klan collective, which he left in 2013.
